1 week from today DOLLA $LICE playing it’s biggest show yet! To celebrate 20 years of Marquee NYC.

This one’s special for me. In the beginning of 2023 I decided to start a house music project from 0 with my good friend Sam. If you know me you know I’ve been rapping on dance music forever. But I wanted to create something that could be JUST that. And to collaborate with new artists. Through 2023 I tried to balance being creative in both projects. managing both of them, doing the marketing for both, handling bookings for both etc . So, to see that the Zak Downtown listeners were still here, and to meet the new DOLLA $LICE fans makes this year special. DONT BE AFRAID TO START SOMETHING NEW EVEN IF YOURE “OLD” This got me motivated to go even harder for both projects in 2024 ❤️🗽
I need some peace and rest. 🧘‍♂️

We launched @dollaslicemusic in December of ‘22 with no real expectations except having fun producing music. We released 5 songs , opened for major house music acts , played a show in Curacao and got over 2 million streams in our first year. Was a trip to look back at all the footage and think it was only 1 year. 🍕 🥂 2024
